<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-13070] unittest antiCompactionSizeTest is flaky</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-13070</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Unittest &lt;tt&gt;org.apache.cassandra.db.compaction.AntiCompactionTest.antiCompactionSizeTest&lt;/tt&gt; is failing from time to time on branch 3.0 (&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/commit/13e939624d21eaf6e16d60b28636125e817ab286&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;13e9396&lt;/a&gt;):&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;    [junit] Testcase: antiCompactionSizeTest(org.apache.cassandra.db.compaction.AntiCompactionTest):    FAILED
    [junit] expected:&amp;lt;1.29786604E8&amp;gt; but was:&amp;lt;1.13623354E8&amp;gt;
    [junit] junit.framework.AssertionFailedError: expected:&amp;lt;1.29786604E8&amp;gt; but was:&amp;lt;1.13623354E8&amp;gt;
    [junit]     at org.apache.cassandra.db.compaction.AntiCompactionTest.antiCompactionSizeTest(AntiCompactionTest.java:164)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Run the single test 21 times:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; i in {0..20}; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;do&lt;/span&gt; echo ==$i; ant testsome -Dtest.name=org.apache.cassandra.db.compaction.AntiCompactionTest -Dtest.methods=antiCompactionSizeTest; echo $i $? &amp;gt;&amp;gt; ~/testresult; done
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;On mac, it passed for 5 times, on linux it passed for 6 times.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
