&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15877345" author="jay.zhuang" created="Wed, 22 Feb 2017 02:46:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I agree that this check is not necessary. Update the patch to remove it.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15879637" author="yukim" created="Thu, 23 Feb 2017 01:10:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks, committed as &lt;tt&gt;51796ea63420f8daa49c9d491588ba9740c6b0d1&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
